      <h2 id="special-thoughts-on-healing-after-losing-a-pet">Special Thoughts on Healing After Losing a Pet</h2>
      <p></p>
<p>Allowing time to grieve is crucial.  Healing takes time, and there is no right or wrong way to feel.  Remember your pet's legacy of love and companionship; this is what endures.</p>
<p>Remember the love, the joy, and the companionship your beloved pet brought into your life. Hold onto those memories.  They are precious, and they will always be a part of you.  Let the love you shared ease the pain, and know that your pet will always be in your heart.</p>
    
  
